  "details": "A weakness has been identified in elunez eladmin up to 2.7. This vulnerability affects unknown code of the file App.java of the component Application Deployment Module. This manipulation of the argument uploadPath causes command injection. Remote exploitation of the attack is possible. The exploit has been made available to the public and could be used for attacks. The project was informed of the problem early through an issue report but has not responded yet.",
